Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要…上路了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:47.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时带上你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.47,0:02:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集合残余舰队 重组阵型
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.01,0:02:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许退缩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.12,0:02:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一战事关 地球的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泽拉·金斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他继承了伊泽尔坎特大人的基因
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.20,0:03:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是拥有最强X-Rounder能力的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.44,0:03:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷酷无情的战士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.57,0:03:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.86,0:03:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:29.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让下可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.99,0:03:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 拜托悠着点用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚修舰长把这艘船交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.56,0:03:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鉴于事态紧急 我们会物尽其用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温蒂 别站着看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:56.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听得见吗 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.68,0:04:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊泽尔坎特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.79,0:04:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类 需要有更好的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你却执迷不悟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.17,0:04:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为做法不对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人没权力鉴别人类 建立什么理想乡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是为了让人活得更有人样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活得也很像人！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.27,0:04:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球圈的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.08,0:04:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星圈的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.85,0:04:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了生存竭尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.04,0:04:48.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法理解吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就算用强硬措施
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会将它实现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这感觉是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.56,0:05:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人损失如此惨重 为何还能这样善战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何应对？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经没有退路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:30.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次从第二月球获得能量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.59,0:05:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射迪格玛泽隆炮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次发射风险极大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本就不是连射武器…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.29,0:05:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事我知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场仗我们输不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.43,0:05:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始供能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.59,0:05:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消灭…高达
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.41,0:06:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:02.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆 小心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从未感知过这种等级的X-Rounder
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 只要高达…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我们齐心合力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.84,0:06:14.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上 C浮游炮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,占上风 能行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希德？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.79,0:07:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可能想占据希德
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.36,0:07:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪格玛泽隆炮能量供应出现异常
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.15,0:07:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么 原因是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:36.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疯了吗 泽拉·金斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,X领域遥感测量数据全部出现异常
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失控？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.91,0:07:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,副热回收系统停止运转
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,供能线路过热
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去 第二月球也难保…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.42,0:07:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即分离拉·格拉密斯与第二月球
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行！ 强制分离系统无法启动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.51,0:08:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要拉上第二月球 踏上自灭之路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.06,0:08:14.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日野司令的AGE-1
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.65,0:08:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装备了等离子潜航导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.54,0:08:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重新出击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.07,0:08:20.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说 司令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算亲手 把维甘…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但机不可失 该做个了结了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.71,0:08:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:36.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样也会牵连第二月球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.36,0:08:38.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.05,0:08:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.19,0:08:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘 你们完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.60,0:08:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想给我们 致命一击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.48,0:08:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是为了今天而活着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:03.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们 赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明日野司令…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.66,0:09:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.21,0:09:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道要发射等离子导弹？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:18.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样做是对的 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.26,0:09:26.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切即将结束
