Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切即将结束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尝尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那儿干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快让开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.70,0:09:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再打下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.37,0:09:58.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荒谬 胜利近在眼前！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起去找
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.07,0:10:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以共存的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:07.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们夺走了我们的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.41,0:10:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发过誓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为保护身边的人们 要成为救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.31,0:10:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火星圈的人也是人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.63,0:10:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们同样在生死线上挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.84,0:10:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们同样是有血有肉的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把对死亡的恐惧 转化成对地球的憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.24,0:10:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 以夺回地球为唯一的生存希望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.24,0:10:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是爷爷想当的救世主吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我战斗到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是为了那些当初没能保护好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 绝对不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.73,0:10:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.14,0:10:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也一定不想看到这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.46,0:11:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…我该怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.05,0:11:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚铃…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.45,0:11:15.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也知道他们很苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.49,0:11:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他们把柚铃…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我让你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 善良的菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.11,0:11:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我没能保护好柚铃！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:44.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅…大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:47.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也原谅…你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚铃…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.60,0:12:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特 漫长的旅途啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确实是个了不起的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.01,0:12:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多…该结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.05,0:12:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.18,0:12:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.91,0:12:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 就算我不动手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.75,0:12:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二月球也将毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.33,0:12:27.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就去救吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,办法只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.59,0:12:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那个球状物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接和第二月球分开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.45,0:12:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么多的数量 再怎么想…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.79,0:12:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 能行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.56,0:12:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以做到 只要大家齐心合力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:13.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令 一切准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球圈与火星圈的所有战士们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.98,0:13:27.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向所有信号范围内的机动战士通话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你们停止战斗听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:31.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.84,0:13:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘的移动殖民地 第二月球将解体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无数生命会逝去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为拯救那些生命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.68,0:13:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有分离即将爆炸的球状部分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非这里的所有人齐心合力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.96,0:13:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.01,0:13:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向地球联邦军与
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:13:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘所有战士通话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.04,0:14:12.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了拯救众多生灵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你们的协助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘士兵们 也被他说服了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.36,0:14:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那老头子确实不同凡响
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.33,0:14:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷终于当上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉…高达
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.55,0:14:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希德？不 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.87,0:15:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.16,0:15:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.64,0:15:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.78,0:15:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.19,0:15:17.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火箭炮型远程光束武器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.78,0:15:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们叫它泰坦火箭炮 好好用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:31.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘基亚 击毁己方机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在继续移动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制服不了它吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特大人已逝 无有对策…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.84,0:15:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我接通联邦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.80,0:15:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.68,0:15:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是拉·格拉密斯要塞司令官
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法尔克·奥克拉姆德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我军的强力机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正失去控制
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.12,0:15:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是指那个大家伙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.67,0:15:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面的机师 是为战斗而生的强化克隆人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他 化作了无法驾驭的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我们 最后的敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.54,0:16:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.97,0:16:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来 继续追击危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.80,0:16:25.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能让它停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.78,0:16:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须有人去结束这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.23,0:16:31.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到要做到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.45,0:16:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.20,0:16:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 战斗已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:54.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到高达和所有联邦机动战士…被歼灭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.37,0:17:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.18,0:17:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘的机动战士也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来帮吉欧了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.19,0:17:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分离作业马上完成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.46,0:18:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此 结束了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.51,0:18:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.09,0:18:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.22,0:19:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.15,0:19:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.19,0:19:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那就是吉欧·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.57,0:19:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的孙子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.28,0:19:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.67,0:19:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了吉欧 辛苦了吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.68,0:19:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德勒尔 我并不想要战争
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.36,0:19:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想营造…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.56,0:19:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们可以活得像人的新世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:19:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:19:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.44,0:20:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界确实改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.73,0:20:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.41,0:20:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我始终相信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.63,0:20:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子就是罗米的转世
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.03,0:20:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他让我们找回了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即将忘记的 作为人的善良
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.03,0:20:33.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊泽尔坎特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.51,0:20:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球就托付给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.45,0:20:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让我们看到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.24,0:20:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人可以像人一样活着的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.33,0:21:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们还要继续生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.98,0:21:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手牵手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.40,0:21:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.40,0:21:17.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一场战争宣告结束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类之后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.72,0:21:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收集AGE系统和EXA-DB的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开发出将火星瘟疫无效化的伊瓦尔斯系统
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.08,0:21:32.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜其所赐 火星圈成为安全的住所
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.24,0:21:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以容纳全部人口的居住空间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.07,0:21:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉·格拉密斯之战过后的 第37个年头
